source.name: San Francisco Wind Monitoring Data - Current
source.description: Data measured by weather stations installed by the SFPUC that have wind monitoring located throughout San Francisco and on SFPUC-owned land. Parameters recorded include: wind speed, wind direction, ambient temperature, and solar irradiance.
